Package: reviz
Title: Visualize Variable Relationships with Model Overlays
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Nathan", "Alexander",
      email = "nathan.alexander@howard.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Create scatterplots of variable relationships with fitted model overlays (linear, loess). Supports coloring or faceting by third variable. Works with any data frame including critstats datasets like africa_data_all.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
